ation\nindex, or the g-index, to measure and compare the skill-acquisition efficiency\nof any intelligence system on a set of real-world tasks. Finally, we evaluate\nthe suitability of some well-known models as general intelligence systems by\ncalculating their g-index scores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 16:59:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2021 18:09:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 03:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 16:16:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
