e\nresearch is to provide with an excellent and free alternative for aeroelastic\nsimulations, that will leverage the use of high-fidelity in the common\npractise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Sep 2021 10:27:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-28"}
